&lt;li&gt;Excellent written and verbal communication skills; ability to present complex issues clearly to non-technical senior stakeholders&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven ability to lead cross-functional remediation efforts and track closure of corrective actions&lt;/li&gt;
