&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;6+ years of experience in risk program management, strategy, management consulting, business operations, or operations program management&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The ability to dig deep into the data and think from first principles while delivering the best results&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to manage multiple stakeholders with varying priorities and drive creative solutions and commitment to a shared goal&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
