&lt;p&gt;This role is part of the Office of the CISO pillar at Stripe. You&#39;ll represent all of Stripe directly to our customers and partners, facilitate conversations with Legal and Security teams, and identify opportunities to enhance our coverage and scalability with tooling and automation.&lt;/p&gt;
