&lt;p&gt;• You are a critical thinker, passionate, self-driven, and detail-oriented&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Preferred qualifications&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;• You&#39;ve developed reports on program performance via dashboards and OKRs, and performed detailed data analysis&lt;/p&gt;
