&lt;li&gt;5+ years of technical program management experience with demonstrated success in security-focused initiatives&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience managing complex technical programs with multiple stakeholders and dependencies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong understanding of security concepts and best practices, particularly in API security, authentication systems, and access controls&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent communication skills with the ability to translate complex technical concepts to various audiences&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven track record of influencing decisions across teams without direct authority&lt;/li&gt;
