&lt;li&gt;Act as an advisor to customers to ensure they’re leveraging the solution effectively&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor and identify usage trends to uncover renewal risks and support greater adoption rates&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate cross-functionally with internal Datadog teams (support, product, finance, and legal)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
