&lt;p&gt;The GTM Operations Associate - Channels &amp;amp; Alliances will join a global team driving Datadog&#39;s next phase of growth. We are interdisciplinary thinkers with diverse backgrounds across consulting, finance, strategy, operations, and technology. Our team partners directly with GTM leaders to improve operational efficiency, support data-driven decision-making, and scale the processes and systems that enable continued growth.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In this role, you will serve as an operational partner to Datadog&#39;s Channels &amp;amp; Alliances organization. You will execute critical business operations, support reporting and business systems, and help scale operational processes across the organization. You will work closely with cross-functional teams to ensure our C&amp;amp;A teams have the tools, data, and operational support they need to be successful. Success in this role requires strong attention to detail, systems thinking, and a passion for improving how teams operate.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;At Datadog, we place value in our office culture - the relationships and collaboration it builds and the creativity it brings to the table. We operate as a hybrid workplace to ensure our Datadogs can create a work-life harmony that best fits them.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you&#39;ll do:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own recurring operational processes that support the global Channels &amp;amp; Alliances organization, ensuring execution is timely, accurate, and scalable.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build, maintain, and enhance Salesforce reports and dashboards to provide visibility into pipeline, partner performance, and other key business metrics.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with C&amp;amp;A, Revenue Operations, Systems, Sales, and other cross-functional teams to improve operational workflows, resolve business issues, and ensure data integrity across systems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate with and evaluate external vendors to support operational processes, systems enhancements, and business initiatives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create and maintain process documentation, playbooks, and standard operating procedures to improve consistency and scalability across the organization.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify opportunities to automate manual processes and leverage AI-enabled tools to improve operational efficiency and reduce administrative work.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as a trusted operational resource for the Channels &amp;amp; Alliances organization, balancing multiple priorities while delivering high-quality support to stakeholders across the business.&lt;/li&gt;
