&lt;li&gt;Maintain inventory of office supplies and ensure timely restocking to support daily operations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Arrange fun and engaging events for employees - both on a monthly cadence and an ad hoc basis&lt;/li&gt;
